b. ChatGPT Assistant using openai\par
Code:\par
import openai\par
openai.api_key = "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"\par
messages = []\par
system_msg = input("What type of chatbot would you like to create?\\n")\par
messages.append(\{"role": "system", "content": system_msg\})\par
print("Your new assistant is ready! Type your query")\par
while input != "quit()":\par
 message = input()\par
 messages.append(\{"role": "user", "content": message\})\par
 response = openai.ChatCompletion.create(model="gpt-3.5-turbo", messages=messages)\par
 reply = response["choices"][0]["message"]["content"]\par
 messages.append(\{"role": "assistant", "content": reply\})\par
 print("\\n" + reply + "\\n")\par
Output:\par
What type of chatbot would you like to create?\par
Nila\rquote s personal chatbot\par
(ctrl enter)\par
Your new assistant is ready!\par
c. CHATBOT CHAT ASSISTANT WEBSITE\par
Code:\par
import openai\par
import gradio\par
openai.api_key = "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"\par
messages = [\{"role": "system", "content": "You are a financial experts that specializes in real\par
estate investment and negotiation"\}]\par
def CustomChatGPT(user_input):\par
 messages.append(\{"role": "user", "content": user_input\})\par
 response = openai.ChatCompletion.create(\par
 model = "gpt-3.5-turbo",\par
 messages = messages\par
 )\par
 ChatGPT_reply = response["choices"][0]["message"]["content"]\par
 messages.append(\{"role": "assistant", "content": ChatGPT_reply\})\par
 return ChatGPT_reply\par
demo = gradio.Interface(fn=CustomChatGPT, inputs = "text", outputs = "text", title =\par
"INTELLIGENT CHATBOT")\par
demo.launch(share=True)\par
